    "body": "- Environment support for arguments of some commands were missed in the rollout of spack environments\r\n- For example, `spack location -i` complains about ambiguous specs, even when it's caused by specs outside the current environment\r\n\r\n- [x] make all commands that need to disambiguate specs restrict the disambiguation to installed packages in the active environment, as users would expect",
